---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Fintech" description="How sentrik enforces PCI DSS, SOC2, and OWASP compliance for fintech teams.">

<section class="uc-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="uc-badge">Use Case</div>
    <h1>PCI DSS + SOC2 + OWASP Compliance for Fintech</h1>
    <p class="uc-sub">Automated security and payment card governance for financial technology teams using AI coding agents.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="uc-content">
  <div class="container uc-inner">
    <h2>The Challenge</h2>
    <p>Fintech companies face triple pressure: ship fast with AI coding tools, pass SOC2 audits with evidence of security controls, and meet PCI DSS requirements for handling payment card data. AI-generated code can introduce OWASP vulnerabilities (SQL injection, hardcoded secrets, auth failures) that manual review misses at scale.</p>

    <h2>How sentrik Helps</h2>

    <div class="feature-list">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Combined PCI DSS + SOC2 + OWASP Scanning</h3>
        <p>Enable all three packs simultaneously &mdash; 54 rules covering cardholder data protection, access control, cryptographic failures, injection, logging, change management, and all 9 SOC2 Trust Services Criteria.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Audit Evidence on Every PR</h3>
        <p>SARIF reports integrate with GitHub Code Scanning. HTML reports with severity charts and compliance checklists serve as SOC2 audit artifacts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Continuous Compliance</h3>
        <p>Gate every PR in CI/CD. Critical and high severity findings block merge. Documentation obligations track non-code compliance items without blocking development.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>GRC Integration &amp; Evidence Export</h3>
        <p>Auto-export evidence to Drata, Vanta, or Secureframe for SOC2 audit workflows. Auditor portals with time-boxed access. Compliance score tracking for continuous readiness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Change Impact &amp; License Compliance</h3>
        <p>Analyze what scope changes ripple through your codebase. SBOM generation tracks all dependencies and license compliance for cardholder data systems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Policy-as-Code</h3>
        <p>Define custom policies beyond regex: &ldquo;no API calls in src/billing/ may use HTTP&rdquo;, &ldquo;all files must have copyright header.&rdquo; Enforce organizational standards automatically.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Quick Start</h2>
    <pre><code>npm install -g sentrik
sentrik add-pack soc2        # OWASP auto-enabled, add SOC2
sentrik add-pack pci-dss     # Add PCI DSS for payment card rules
sentrik scan</code></pre>

    <div class="uc-cta">
      <a href="/blog/getting-started-in-5-minutes" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-outline">View Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>

<style>
  .screenshot { width: 100%; max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .uc-hero { padding: 6rem 0 3rem; text-align: center; }
  .uc-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .uc-sub { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .uc-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .uc-inner h2 { margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .uc-inner p { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .feature-list { display: grid; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .feature-item { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .feature-item h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .feature-item p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; }
  .uc-inner pre { margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .uc-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>
